00:45:38.180 --> 00:45:39.060
There was another man

00:45:39.060 --> 00:45:40.820
known as Al-Walid ibn al-Mughirah.

00:45:40.820 --> 00:45:42.820
He was the uncle of Abu Jahl.

00:45:42.820 --> 00:45:44.660
He also had a lot

00:45:45.940 --> 00:45:47.860
to do in terms of harm

00:45:47.860 --> 00:45:49.540
against the Muslims.

00:45:49.540 --> 00:45:51.700
He went to Rasulullah

00:45:51.700 --> 00:45:52.900
sallallahu alayhi wasallam

00:45:52.900 --> 00:45:55.300
and he heard verses of the Quran.

00:45:56.100 --> 00:45:57.620
He came back to his people

00:45:58.180 --> 00:45:59.140
